00:02:26.430 --> 00:02:31.950
Fiberio is a touchscreen that senses fingerprints
freeing users from having to carry any other

00:02:31.950 --> 00:02:33.500
type of identification.

00:02:33.500 --> 00:02:38.360
The fiber optic plate the screen uses gives
it the ability to both display images and

00:02:38.360 --> 00:02:40.860
sense fingerprints at the same time.

00:02:40.860 --> 00:02:44.740
Applications for this could be in the workplace
where based on your fingerprints the system

00:02:44.740 --> 00:02:48.390
would only allow you to access data that you
are given cleared for.

