00:03:09.860 --> 00:03:15.200
ERO is a concrete recycling robot that disassembles
concrete structures using water jets to crack

00:03:15.200 --> 00:03:18.610
the surface of the concrete and then suck
up the debris.

00:03:18.610 --> 00:03:22.980
The ERO makes the destruction of concrete
cleaner and more effective because previous

00:03:22.980 --> 00:03:27.950
systems created huge dusty mounds of concrete
and metal to be sorted through and it also

00:03:27.950 --> 00:03:31.590
saves a lot of water by recycling it back
through itself.

